node.text:
The one and only @LakeForkGuy gives us a first look at the all new Googan Rods in collaboration with @CatchCompany. Exclusively available for Pre-Order now @karlsbaitandtackle
#GooganTakeover #GooganRods
The Googan Squad Banger is money at triggering a reaction bite when it is deflected off cover!🔥 What are some other lures you like to throw around cover? 🎣 #googansquad
